{"tid":958332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"豬瘟惹的禍？ 她驚恐PO中國(廣東)漢堡肉 網友：超噁快吐了！","createTime":"2018-12-27T17:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T12:42:40.000Z","uid":35790,"like":86,"dislike":171,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"4fab078229486ab14bcfecaa2b71b92af09b5d15","tid":958332,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T17:14:17.000Z","msg":"豬瘟惹的禍？ 她驚恐PO中國漢堡肉 網友：超噁快吐了！<br />\n<br />\n出一張照片，「朋友在廣東吃到這樣的肉，想請教廣大的廢友，這肉發生了什麼事...」，照片中可見，漢堡肉片上布滿大大小小的「坑洞」，而且還被咬了好幾口。原PO直呼，看到這照片密集恐懼症快爆發了，朋友更是「食慾全消，不敢吃，只好浪費食物了。」<br />\n<br />\n照片曝光後，引起網友熱議，不少人想到這肉排恐怕就是中國非洲豬瘟疫情造成的，紛紛留言，「應該是最近病豬肉那件事 好噁心」、「起雞皮疙瘩了我」、「這是豬瘟的肉嗎，還是別吃了吧」、「其中有一個洞還吐出橘色的汁...」、「這是病毒豬....」、「超超超超級無敵噁心 快要吐了啦」。<br />\n<br />\n但也有網友解釋，這應該是豬肉長「淋巴瘤」，通常是「豬生病硬打針、打抗生素，才會這樣子的」，通常都會丟掉。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php2tiBoS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php2tiBoS.jpg&h=16d8add2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/2655378\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F2655378&d=2Fzy6X4tYhsMvz%2B9IN6ygzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=dceda47f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F2655378&h=6b4b247a\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/2655378</a>"},{"pid":"3999e63f9fe642ac5ee56627a90e185a24d65d71","tid":958332,"uid":55924,"like":402,"dislike":4,"score":398,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T17:15:09.000Z","msg":"屌你加慎入啦"},{"pid":"016d0d311826d8bd570fe4f43f616095d44291c3","tid":958332,"uid":35790,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T17:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707b01e5ef734b2caaaf9edb6fa295c94a6e6558","tid":958332,"uid":59764,"like":190,"dislike":5,"score":185,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T17:15:5